
{ Disabling IPv6 #disable

  In Ubuntu, IPv6 can be disabled in → Linux/fhs/etc/sysctl_conf
code {
net.ipv6.conf.all.disable_ipv6 = 1
net.ipv6.conf.default.disable_ipv6 = 1
net.ipv6.conf.lo.disable_ipv6 = 1
code }


  Apparently, → development/Apache/Hadoop needs IPv6 to be → development/Apache/Hadoop/index#ipv6

  sa: http://askubuntu.com/questions/440649/how-to-disable-ipv6-in-ubuntu-14-04[How to disable IPv6 in Ubuntu 14.04?]

}
